# ARMcreative Portfolio Website

**Version:** 1.0  
**Author:** ARMcreative  
**License:** MIT

---

A modern, premium portfolio website built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Dark mode first design with glassmorphism effects
- Smooth scroll navigation (Lenis-like implementation)
- Custom cursor with hover effects
- Particle background animation with mouse interaction
- Scroll reveal animations with stagger effects
- 3D tilt effect on cards
- Magnetic button effects
- Parallax on mouse move
- Typing animation
- Portfolio filtering
- Testimonial carousel with drag/swipe support
- Mobile responsive
- SEO optimized
- Accessibility compliant

## Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Custom Properties, Glassmorphism, Animations)
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)

## Getting Started

Simply open `index.html` in your browser. No build tools required.

